public static void reThrowClassCastExceptionIfNeeded(java.lang.ClassCastException e)
The HierarchicalConfiguration class of Apache Commons Configuration throws a certain ClassCastException if presented with a numerical key. This particular case shall be supressed but all others be re-thrown.
